{
  "chapter": 152,
  "chapter_summary": "泾水西岸田猎大营，纪嫣然一眼看穿高陵君火攻袭营的策略，项少龙决定加强监视。昌文君拉众人到骑射场凑热闹，嬴盈三箭连珠射中红心，气势逼人。纪嫣然为维护夫君颜面，亲自出手以背身反手连珠箭技压全场，将嬴盈比下去。项少龙被小盘召见，藉纠正射箭姿势之机取血以备滴血认亲，并展示飞针绝技震慑吕不韦一众。小盘与项少龙、李斯密商应对高陵君叛乱和吕不韦阴谋之策，决定让小盘亲自挂帅立威。嫪毐来传太后召见，小盘临行前深情叮嘱师父保重。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "高陵君来袭时，必会先使人烧王营的木寨和离河最远的营帐，由于近日吹的是东南风，火势浓烟逼来，我们唯有渡河往泾水北岸去躲避。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "嫣然真高明，一眼看穿高陵君的策略，所以只要密切监视，看看高陵君或吕不韦的人何时为营帐涂上火油一类的东西，当知道他们发动的时刻。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们到下面骑射场去凑热闹啊！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位嫂子福安，唉！我对少龙真是妒忌得差点要了我的小命。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "昌文君忙完了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "太后和储君刚安顿好，琴太傅被太后召去说话，嘱小将来通知各位嫂子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "text": "你去凑热闹吧！我想回营好好睡上一觉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们玩耍去了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下一个轮到谁啊？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们女儿军的首席射手神箭一出，谁还敢来献丑？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_dan_er",
      "speaker_name": "鹿丹儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领的腿伤好了吗？听说你挡箭的剑术天下无双，不知射箭的功夫如何？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先让嫣然试试好吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "杀杀我妹子的傲气也好！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是时候了！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅！寡人的成绩还不错吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "若储君多用点手，少用点眼，成绩当会更好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "射箭最讲究眼力，多用点手是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有蚊子！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "储君莫要分心，射箭之道，手、眼固须配合，但以手瞄却胜过以眼瞄，这是由于眼看到目标，还要通知自己的心，再由心去指挥手，隔了多重。但若以手去瞄准的话，便少去重重阻隔，看！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让飞针留在靶上，寡人要带回宫内作个纪念，这三天就让它们像现在那样子好了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难怪太傅的飞针如此既快且准，原来是用手的感觉去掷。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙这一手飞针，可说是空前绝后。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lv_niang_rong",
      "text": "蓉儿！现在你该知项大人的本领了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅这手飞针绝技，定要传我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难怪项大人能屡脱险境，实非侥幸，这些飞针比弩箭更难闪躲，更不用说拿剑去挡格了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "储君和李大人不用夸奖我，昨晚我刚从鬼门关打个转回来，却全靠侥幸。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人的胆子一个比一个大，究竟视寡人为何物？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "储君息怒，项大人对此事必有妥善应付之法。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "既知高陵君叛党袭营的时间，我自可调动兵马，将他们一网打尽，教他们全无用武之地。而营地这边，微臣希望储君能亲自挂帅，调军遣将，一方面把高陵君的人全体成擒，另一方面则把吕不韦制个贴伏，露上一手，那以后还有人敢不把储君放在眼内吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人果是胸有成竹，不知计将安出？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "这事须凭精确情报和当时的形势厘定，微臣会与李大人保持联系，摸清形势，再由储君定夺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一切照项卿家所奏请的去办吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天太后对寡人说，吕不韦要把最疼爱的三女儿委身于项卿家，寡人还以为吕不韦转了性子，原来其中竟有如此狠辣的阴谋。哈！莫傲这家伙死到临头仍不自知，真是笑破寡人的肚皮。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "太后有请储君。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "知道了！内侍长请回，寡人立即就来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项卿家是否准备迎娶吕不韦的宝贝女儿呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_zheng",
      "text": "吕不韦若见我死不了，绝不会把女儿嫁我，不过此事由他头痛好了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "寡人知道怎么办了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父小心，若你有什么三长两短，这天地将了无生趣。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 152,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    }
  ],
